msgid ""
"The algorithm operates by testing the layer's extent in every known "
"reference system and then listing any for which the bounds would be near the"
" target area if the layer was in this projection."
msgstr ""
"Algoritmen fungerar genom att testa lagrets utsträckning i alla kända "
"referenssystem och sedan lista alla för vilka gränserna skulle vara nära "
"målområdet om lagret var i denna projektion."

